Jesus spoke in ways some found difficult
to understand.

00:00:04.270 --> 00:00:07.810
And he use many devices when preaching
and teaching

00:00:07.810 --> 00:00:11.400
for instance Jesus spoke of the cup.

00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:16.620
Remember the cup from a earlier episode,
we talked about that before, remember?

00:00:16.620 --> 00:00:18.599
Oh, thank you.

00:00:18.599 --> 00:00:22.570
Or perhaps he use the plate.

00:00:22.570 --> 00:00:25.730
Remember the plate? Oh.

00:00:25.730 --> 00:00:29.430
Thank you. The cup and the plate they kinda go together, right?

00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:32.900
sure!

00:00:32.910 --> 00:00:36.050
Yeah right, sure, or maybe he used the bowl.

